# Account & Data Deletion Request - Future Focus Test App

To request deletion of your account and associated data from the Future Focus Test app, please follow the steps below.

## How to request account deletion
Email us at: **futurefocustest@gmail.com**

Subject: `Account Deletion Request`

Include your registered email address in the message.

## Data that will be deleted
- Email
- Name
- Test results
- Firebase authentication records

All related personal data is deleted from our Firebase database.

## Processing time
Deletion requests are processed within **7 days**.  
Backup logs may remain for **30 days** for security reasons.

